Description:
Great Waterfront Location – Easy City Access - Call now for a discussion
Work, play or just relax. Apartment 407 at No. 1 Collins Wharf provides all the options. Great for the investor, owner/occupier or an amazing city getaway. Stroll across the road to the Free Tram, walk along the Yarra River and beautiful Victoria Harbour or take advantage of the iconic Dock Library nearby. Walking distance to supermarkets, medical facilities, cafes & restaurants and handy to South Wharf and District Docklands shopping, Southbank, Etihad Stadium and the many attractions of the Melbourne CBD.
This nomination opportunity at Victoria Harbour’s newest address, No.1 Collins Wharf. provides entry to one of Melbourne’s prestige waterfront locations. Open plan living, sophisticated finishes, gleaming kitchen and bathroom, spacious bedroom, quality appliances, air-conditioning, secure access.
Yarra River outlook from bedroom and living areas opening onto a wide balcony offering an unrivalled waterfront atmosphere.
Superb resident’s facilities include sophisticated entry lobby, private resident’s swimming pool, gym and resident’s entertainment spaces. No.1 Collins Wharf - Melbourne’s new waterfront icon.
Insights: 141 other 1 bedroom unit in Docklands have recently been sold.

Description:
Gold Tower: Standout offering with brilliant harbour views
Sure to catch the eye of savvy Docklands investors as well as city professionals wanting a stylish and modern pad moments to the CBD, this smart and sophisticated 1 bedroom apartment is a sleek jewel in the ‘Gold Tower’ of the Aqui development.
Major highlights include a balcony with phenomenal views of Victoria Harbour, relaxed living/dining with floor-to-ceiling windows, stone kitchen with quality Asko appliances, bedroom with a mirrored built-in robe and study nook, luxury bathroom with laundry, and reverse cycle cooling (including in both the living zone and bedroom).
You also get a secure car space, and access to a 25m indoor pool, spa, sauna, gym, library, private meeting rooms, and rooftop garden. Seconds to The District Docklands, waterside restaurants, Marvel Stadium, Ron Barassi Snr Park, and the 30, 70, and 86 trams taking you across Melbourne.
Please contact Vicky Leong on 0452 485 860 to arrange an exclusive inspection.

Description:
Experience Bright and Stylish Docklands Living
Simple in design yet spectacular in scope, this leading-edge 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment sets a noteworthy benchmark for contemporary Docklands living. With convenience covered, take an effortless stroll to Southern Cross Station, Crown Entertainment Complex, and the restaurants and bars of New Quay with free city trams on your doorstep. you're also moments to Docklands Park, The Hub @ Docklands, and countless great cafes.
Prominently positioned on the 28th floor of the tightly held Victoria Point tower, this light filled property delivers open plan lounge and dining zone, stone kitchen with stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher, ample sized balcony off the living zone which has panoramic views of Port Phillip Bay, both large sized bedrooms with built-in robes, well-appointed bathrooms, and a European laundry.
Other features include a secured parking space plus storage cage, video intercom entry, ducted heating/cooling, concierge, and access to gym.
This is an opportunity not to be missed. Please call Peter Doan on 0402 959 842 for an inspection.
* Photo identification will be required upon entering the property at the inspection time.

Description:
Supersized Indoor/Outdoor Living with Unrivalled Views
A superior celebration of free-flowing space, oversized outdoor entertaining, and breathtaking city and blue-water views, this stunning 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom home makes the most of high-end, designer finishes so close to the CBD. With convenience covered, take an effortless stroll to Southern Cross Station, Crown Entertainment Complex, and the restaurants and bars of New Quay with free city trams on your doorstep.
The "flow-through" design of this apartment will captivate from the very first step inside with a tempting trio of balconies offering light and airy cross-ventilation. Discover an open living and dining area revolving around a sleek, stone-topped kitchen boasting Miele appliances and an entertainers' island bench. Floor-to-ceiling glass bookends the apartment with a large, sheltered balcony spectacularly perched over Victoria Harbour. Directly opposite, a supersized terrace faces northeast with simply showstopping city and blue-water bay views. This outdoor entertaining area is a true game-changer, capable of entertaining hundreds at a time! Both bedrooms are especially large with mirrored built-in robes and balcony access, while the main showcases a sparkling, twin-vanity ensuite. A luxurious, family-sized bathroom offers a bath, fully tiled, walk-in shower and a marble-topped vanity.
Comprehensive features consist of a separate laundry including a dryer, ducted heating and cooling, roller blinds, ample storage, and a pair of secure, side-by-side car spaces plus storage cage, building manager, video intercom entry, and premium lifestyle facilities including a fully equipped gym. This is truly living!
* Photo identification will be required upon entering the property at the inspection time.

Description:
Inspired and contemporary with superb north views from The Quays
Enhanced by imposing and open views to the north and an enchanting modern sensibility thanks to the high end quality and luxury fittings in the exclusive Quays complex, this memorable two bedroom apartment means your search for the ultimate Docklands retreat is over.
You’ll be welcomed by the fantastic size and relaxed feel of the central living and meals zone, which has direct entry to the long balcony where stunning north and east views will become part of your daily life. The balcony is also accessed via both charming bedrooms which each have built-in robe storage.
The stone kitchen promises an easy care set up while still offering all the bells and whistles including stainless steel Smeg appliances, high gloss splashback and plenty of storage. Other fantastic property features include a gleaming bathroom with vibrant mosaic tiling and a European laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom and secure car space.
The exceptional facilities of the Quays complex will put a smile on your face, and include a Health Club with pool, spa, sauna, gym and yoga studio, Resident’s Club with library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room and cinema lounge and a rooftop garden with BBQ and dining facilities.
Explore the new surrounds of the NewQuay precinct, which offers an abundance of amazing attractions. You’re an easy walk to terrific restaurants including Mama Rumaan, Woolshed, and Bhoj Restaurants just to name a few, while you’re also close to the new The District Docklands, Etihad Stadium, Victoria Harbour precinct, trams and Southern Cross Station.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to arrange an exclusive viewing.
Internal area
54m²

Description:
Unprecedented river views in timeless Flinders Wharf
With an abundance of modern class and offering all the space you’ve dreamed of to enjoy the apartment lifestyle on the river that you’ve always deserved, this unique 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom residence on the 6th floor of the desired and sort after Flinders Wharf building (next door to the WTC) is an opportunity that rarely comes around and one not to be missed.
This elegant apartment has all your bases covered, from an ultra-spacious main living and meals area to the oversized south-facing covered entertainer’s balcony, which boasts 4 different entry points with spectacular Yarra River & Seafarers Bridge views that will never be built out. The modern Caesarstone kitchen offers up a practical breakfast bar along with additional storage options with European stainless steel appliances including gas.
The master bedroom is just one of the highlights of the apartment and features a study nook or make up area with balcony access, luxurious Poliform style walk through robe that leads to a large sleek ensuite with dual vanity. Further embrace two other bedrooms with BIRs, large duel entry central bathroom, bonus powder room, separate laundry, ducted heating and cooling, ceiling fans, secure intercom and car space as well as multiple integrated LED televisions pre-mounted on walls. Proving that this property is actually a home with exquisite water views, with an easy wearing artistic epoxy flooring which been installed throughout and is warm to the touch. This apartment has an enormous 157 sqm (approx.) of amazing space both inside and out. Other stand out features include 24 hour concierge and security, recreation area boasting indoor heated pool with gym, spa, sauna, steam room and a large visitors car park.
You get to enjoy all the delights of a dream location, opposite South Wharf Promenade and the Melbourne Exhibition & Convention Centre. Within the free tram zone, you’re only minutes from South Melbourne market and in the middle of the action surrounded with world class bars and restaurants, Batman Park, Southern Cross Station and immediate direct freeway access less than 1km away.
To arrange an inspection, please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 or Lynn Lum on 0474 044 293.

BEAUTIFUL ONE OF A KIND APARTMENT
2901/100 HARBOUR ESPLANADE, DOCKLANDS
A once in a lifetime opportunity beckons in the heart of the Docklands with this remarkable 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2 car spaces apartment. Enormous both inside and out and oozing opulence with an expansive living zone, 3 spacious bedrooms, and approximately 120 sqm of terrace with stunning views, this flawless gem is near Marvel Stadium and a plethora of Docklands attractions.
Accommodation: Towering floor-to-ceiling windows, plush surfaces, and a sense of gracious style underline this unique residence, which sits on approximately 120 sqm internally, highlighted by the expansive living area with adjoining kitchen boasting Miele appliances and an island benchtop. All bedrooms are stylish and spacious, none more so than the master bed which has private access to the terrace and lush ensuite.

Description:
Sky-High Luxury Reveals Stunning Harbour and Bay Views
Boasting breathtaking blue-water views over Victoria Harbour and Port Phillip Bay, live the life you love in this ultra-spacious and super-stylish 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment so close to the heart of the city. Enjoy a harbourside lifestyle with waterfront restaurants, Marvel Stadium, South Wharf shopping, Southern Cross trains and free CBD trams on your doorstep.
Positioned on the 19th floor of the sought-after Victoria Point complex, discover a stone-topped kitchen with stainless-steel appliances including a dishwasher, flowing freely through to a wonderfully open living and dining area. The impressive amount of space on offer is accentuated by the imposing panels of glass that encase the apartment. Wonderfully window-walled and dramatically angular, take a pause and immerse yourself in the awe-inspiring water and neighbourhood views, just as captivating by day or night. Those same views are shared on a sheltered balcony with access from the main bedroom, a stunning showpiece with dual-sided, mirrored built-in robes and a twin-vanity ensuite featuring a fully tiled, oversized shower. The second bedroom is also mirror-robed, serviced by a deluxe bathroom showcasing a bath, walk-in shower and a stone-topped vanity.
Take full advantage of secure undercover parking plus a storage cage, a concealed laundry with a Fisher and Paykel dryer, ducted heating and cooling, roller blinds over openable windows, and secure intercom entry. Enjoy exclusive access to an on-site building manager, concierge, and first-class, resort-style facilities including a fully equipped gym and heated pool.
* Photo identification will be required upon entering the property at the inspection time.

Description:
Mosaic: Low-Rise Luxury with Private Parkland Views
Brilliantly bursting with free-flowing space and energising views, this stunning 2 bedroom apartment in the tightly held, low-rise Mosaic complex, highlights affordable, low-maintenance luxury in a convenient city-edge location. The luxury living extends downstairs, moments from Victoria Harbour, Woolworths shopping, Marvel Stadium, and a tantalising choice of quality restaurants and cafes.
Serenely set on the 4th floor, this light-filled apartment showcases far-reaching open-plan living and dining, adjoining a stone-topped Blanco kitchen with an imposing, waterfall-edged breakfast bar. The cleverly designed layout is framed by floor-to-ceiling glass spilling outside to an undercover balcony providing shelter, shade and uninterrupted views of Docklands Park, Marvel Stadium and the dramatic backdrop of Melbourne's city skyline. This instantly calming space will be used on a daily basis, catching afternoon sea breezes with ease. Generously sized, both bedrooms are serviced by a fully tiled bathroom boasting an oversized, walk-in shower and a stone-finished vanity, with the main bedroom showcasing mirrored built-in robes.
Neatly nestled in the heart of Docklands, take advantage of secure parking plus storage cage, concealed laundry with dryer, integrated storage solutions, split-system heating/cooling, secure intercom and low body corporate. This is truly living!
* Photo identification will be required upon entering the property at the inspection time.

Description:
Price Improvement - Two floors of spacious and beautifully stylish town living
Boasting two exceptional levels of generous and ultra-modern living which will excite a variety of buyers who want to enjoy the best of the Yarra’s Edge, this sublime 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom residence with a double remote garage is the ultimate Docklands house!
Featuring a superior build by Mirvac and with a unique floorplan (only 14 of these layouts exist with no more to be built), this dual level haven is filled with brilliant highlights. The downstairs lounge and dining zone is open and expansive, with this area feeding into the deluxe stone kitchen complete with soft-closing drawers and Miele/Asko stainless steel appliances. The kitchen further includes a large casual meals space.
Upstairs is reserved for all four bedrooms. One of these is the sensational master bedroom which has memorable space, walk-through robes, dazzling ensuite, and leafy green views, while three of the other bedrooms have BIRs including one bedroom which has its own private balcony. The top floor also comes with a quality main bathroom.
Further townhouse additions include a sizeable entertainer’s courtyard with open and covered areas plus a separate drying space, downstairs powder room, laundry room, ducted heating and cooling, under stairs storage, rainwater tank, secure alarm and the garage with storage accessed from Portal Lane. There are no owner’s corporation fees with this property with exclusive access to the Wharf Club which offers yoga, pilates, and fitness classes along with a gym and pool for a small fortnightly fee.
This growing area of Yarra’s Edge is set to experience both retail and warehouse revitalisation. You’re also positioned close to terrific local parks, South Wharf Promenade, DFO Shopping, Capital City Trail, IGA X-Press supermarket, and CBD and Port Melbourne attractions.

Description:
Boutique living at its best!
The 'Mosaic' is Docklands incredibly popular boutique low rise residential nine storey complex. It has been built to the highest of standards and positioned to take full aspects of natural lighting and scenery, with dual aspects which allow beautiful landscapes. With only four apartments per floor and two on the ninth floor, this development offers a heightened level of exclusivity. Perfect for any owner occupier or investor!
Located on the 5th floor is this immaculate two bedroom apartment each with built in robes and the main with its own ensuite whilst the second bedroom shares the contemporary bathroom. The gourmet kitchen with stone bench tops and stainless steel appliances (Blanco) adjoins the spacious open plan living/dining area that spills out onto one of the two wide balconies.
Conveniently situated close to restaurants, shopping, Marvel Stadium, Southern Cross Station and within a few minutes drive to Melbourne's CBD, this apartment has all that you need!
Other features include one secure car space, separate laundry facilities, reverse cycle air-con/heating units, internal storage space, security entrance, low body corporate fees and easy accessibility to the public transport nearby.

Description:
Entertainers Delight
Located in the Aero dynamic Watergate residential complex is an outstanding 2 bedroom apartment taking advantage of the corner position of the North Tower.
Flaunting a massive balcony, this apartment features an open plan dining area adjoining a galley kitchen with white colour themed cabinetry, stone benchtop, integrated stainless steel appliances including Gas stove top, electric oven and dishwashing machine.
Two spacious bedrooms, with built in robes share the stylish central bathroom incorporating laundry space. Floor to ceiling double glazed windows enable plenty of natural light.
Other features of the apartment include
• Ducted reverse cycle heating and cooling
• Security entrance and intercom entry
• Car park on title
• Cross ventilation
The complex includes
• 3 lane heated lap pool with spa
• Gymnasium and sauna
• Function room
• On site manager
Located within the free tram zone, close to Southern Cross station and freeway system.
Shop to your hearts content at South Wharf or stroll into the CBD to extend your shopping experience. Superb cafes and eateries in close vicinity or do your grocery shopping at the Woolworths down the road to prepare a home cooked meal.

Description:
Luxurious Northern Riverside Penthouse with two car parks
“EXPRESSIONS OF INTEREST CLOSING SATURDAY 9th FEBRUARY 2019 at 3pm”
Presiding grandly over the most magical views of the Yarra River and the CBD, this exclusive, 2 bedroom apartment is the quintessentially sophisticated inner-city lifestyle pad. Imagine a lifestyle in which you wander towards Crown Entertainment Complex for some of the city’s finest bars and dining or where you can wander in the other direction along absolute riverfront trails and parklands for a sense of tranquillity that is almost surreal for this location.
Spectacular in every regard, with a captivating angular design, this fifth floor / top floor home is architecturally brilliant and combines a breath-taking north-facing perspective with an unparalleled lifestyle experience. Fully utilising its top-floor position in this boutique, low rise block, the home evokes the feel of a penthouse and offers residents access to an impressive suite of lifestyle amenities that includes a swimming pool, gymnasium and sauna.
The home presents a particularly spacious open-plan living area equipped with granite benchtops that include a mobile island bench, as well as a Miele cooktop, an integrated refrigerator and integrated dishwasher. Savvy investors with appreciate the generous lounge / dining, two stunning balconies and well-separated bedrooms – one with ensuite - ensuring a breadth of market appeal.
Discerning down-sizers and ‘lock and leavers’ will not only relish proximity to Docklands, Southbank and the CBD, but also premium security, video entry and the luxury of two side by side parking spaces which are conveniently on the same level as the home.
Additional features includes two designer bathrooms, robes in each bedroom, central heating and cooling and a storage cage as well as access to the fitness facilities at rekdek gym.
What a unique lifestyle offering right on the fringe of Melbourne’s thriving heart!
